extends layout

block content
    .container
        h3 Cars available from: #{startDate} to #{endDate}
    .container
        .row
        each car in cars
            .col-md-5
                h4 Name: #{car.name}
                h4 Model: #{car.model}
                img.image(src=car.img_url)
                hr
                h4 Vin number: #{car.vin_number}
                h4 Price per day: $#{car.price_day}
                hr
                h4 Final price: $#{car.price_day * days} for #{days} days.
                p
                    | Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod. Donec sed odio dui.
                p

                if (user)
                    form(method='POST' action=car.reservation_url)
                        input#start_date.form-control(type='hidden' name='start_date' value=startDate)
                        input#end_date.form-control(type='hidden' name='end_date' value=endDate)

                        button.btn.btn-default(type='submit') Book now!
                if(!user)
                    h4 Login to book
                br
                br
                br
